The date is relative to the Proleptic Gregorian Calendar. If year is 0, the DateTime is considered not to have a specific year. month and day must have valid, non-zero values. Consider using `Timestamp` message for physical time instead. If your use case also would like to store the user's timezone, that can be done in another field.
